title: Takizawa Paperweight
description:
Paperweights inspired by pebbles, made by joining stunning plywood pieces in a patchwork pattern. Constructed by hand in Japan from unique paper-wood material, each pebble is composed of thin pieces of recycled colored paper layered between slices of wood veneer. Light and smooth to the touch.

  • Dimensions:  3 1/2 x 2 3/5 x 1 3/10 in.
